data.description: Beautifully updated former model home in Teravista! New level 4 granite throughout kitchen and bathrooms. New slate floors installed on the 1st floor and staircase landing. 3/4" Oak wood floors installed on stairs, hallway and media room upstairs. Media rm added with built in's for tv and mini fridge. New custom interior paint, new dishwasher w 2 yr warranty remaining, entire house has new water filtration system, 10x10 new shed, and extended patio slab. Elegant floor plan that works well for families
